(## 1. Purpose) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This document explains how the project is structured, how the components fit together, and how the dashboard works end to end.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(It is intended for:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- developers who want to understand the codebase,) Tj
T*
(- researchers who want to describe the system in a paper,) Tj
T*
(- maintainers who need to extend or debug the workflow,) Tj
T*
(- reviewers who want a precise technical overview.) Tj
