(## 2. System Architecture at a Glance) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The project is organized into four layers:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Browser frontend.) Tj
T*
(2. Flask backend server.) Tj
T*
(3. Core screening and storage package.) Tj
T*
(4. Supporting assets, tools, and research files.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The browser handles user interaction. The backend handles validation, scoring, persistence, and PDF export. The Python package contains the reusable screening logic. The tools and data directories support training, evaluation, and publication.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
